The rolls themselves should happen between 3 classes: Die, DiceBag and Roll


DiceBag:
	responsible for parsing roll calls
	parses formatted information to Die class
	
Die Specification:
	responsible for random number calls
	allows specification of random number generator/engine
	Generates Roll objects

Roll:
	Stores information on a particular roll call, including relevant environment context
	overloaded __str__ function gives "pretty" roll results
